      <p>HI is extremely common, appearing in over 1,000 words. It starts HIT, HIM, HIS, HILL, HIDE, HIGH, HIKE and appears mid-word in CHILD, THINK, WITHIN, MACHINE, VEHICLE, and EXHIBIT. WHISKEY (20 pts) and HIGHWAY (20 pts) are elite plays. THINKING (16 pts) and MACHINE (14 pts) use common tiles for premium mid-game scores. HIT (6 pts) clears the H tile quickly.</p>

