        <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg bg-gray-800 border border-gray-700 text-sm"><span class="text-white font-bold">WHISKEY</span><span class="text-blue-400 text-xs">20 pts</span></span>
        <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg bg-gray-800 border border-gray-700 text-sm"><span class="text-white font-bold">EXHIBIT</span><span class="text-blue-400 text-xs">19 pts</span></span>
        <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg bg-gray-800 border border-gray-700 text-sm"><span class="text-white font-bold">ACHIEVE</span><span class="text-blue-400 text-xs">15 pts</span></span>
        <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg bg-gray-800 border border-gray-700 text-sm"><span class="text-white font-bold">HIGHWAY</span><span class="text-blue-400 text-xs">20 pts</span></span>
        <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg bg-gray-800 border border-gray-700 text-sm"><span class="text-white font-bold">ARCHIVE</span><span class="text-blue-400 text-xs">15 pts</span></span>
        <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg bg-gray-800 border border-gray-700 text-sm"><span class="text-white font-bold">THINKING</span><span class="text-blue-400 text-xs">16 pts</span></span>
      </div>

      <div class="not-prose my-6 p-5 rounded-xl border border-blue-500/30 bg-blue-950/20">
        <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-blue-400 uppercase tracking-wider mb-2">🎯 Key Takeaway</p>
        <p class="text-base text-gray-200">HI provides <span class="text-white font-medium">1,000+ words with multiple 20-point elite plays</span>. WHISKEY and HIGHWAY (20 pts each) are top targets. THINKING (16 pts) and MACHINE (14 pts) offer premium mid-game options from common rack tiles.</p>
